data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home on OVER AN ACRE lot in "Hummingbird Place" east of Fayetteville!  New kitchen counter tops, new Dishwasher, new Microwave in this 2100 sq. ft. living area home. Large Great Room with fireplace and French Door, spacious Breakfast Nook off of kitchen! HUGE BONUS ROOM and oversized two car garage as clean as can be...  Much of the acre of land is wooded, and all is on quiet cul-de-sac.  Enjoy the peace and quiet of the country, yet only minutes back to the city!  Adjoining acre lot is also available for sale at $39,900, and owner would consider a "package price/sale" if buyer wants both.
